# Claude local state — ignore everything under .claude/ by default …
.claude/*
# … but commit the vetted-public agent skills as real files (explicit allowlist).
# Re-include the dir before excluding its children so the leaf negations can reach;
# fails safe — a forgotten !line means a public skill is merely missing, never a
# private one leaked.
!.claude/skills/
.claude/skills/*
!.claude/skills/tmp-companion-frontend/
!.claude/skills/tmp-companion-catalog/
!.claude/skills/tmp-companion-write-safety/
!.claude/skills/tmp-companion-device-ops/